    <text id="A8027T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>J. Beck inquires about the purchase of several slaves.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1858-02-08">Feb 8/58</date>
                        <name type="place">Deerfield</name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>Mr Mc.cue Dear Sir</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>I have Caused Mr Clayton to Make a Number of <unclear>hundrd</unclear> if I Can
                    Now make one--I <orig reg="believe">Beleve</orig>--I Could effect a
                    Compromise--I have had Several Conversations with the parties &amp; think
                    that I Could get a <orig reg="fair">fare</orig> Chance for you the parties are
                    well able to pay &amp; I would Like to <unclear>Rec'd</unclear> a Small mite</p>
                <p>is this any thing Like amounts<lb/>the <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> owned Boy $1600.<hi
                        rend="underline">00</hi><lb/>Mary &amp; Child 1550.00 7
                    <unclear>oathers</unclear> 4200.00 7350.00<lb/> Deduct the <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
                    <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> Boy <hi rend="underline">1600.00</hi><lb/>amount <unclear>of C.
                        o</unclear> Negros 3{5750.00<lb/> {1916.66 =</p>
                <p>I have intimated no offer<lb/>must have your proposition</p>
                <p>all must be Strictly Confidential or no Compromise</p>
                <p><orig reg="please answer">pleas anser</orig> Soon</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>yours Respectfully</salute>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="underline">J Beck</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
